"<em>Fokus √ľ√ß√ľn klik:</em>P…ônc…ôr…ô daxilin…ô v…ô ya baŇülńĪńüńĪna klikl…ôndikd…ô "
"aktivl…ôŇüir. Siz ola bilsin ki, bununla baŇüqa …ôm…ôliyyat sisteml…ôrind…ôn "
"tanńĪŇüsńĪnńĪ."

#: windows.cpp:96
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<em>Click to focus (mouse precedence):</em> Mostly the same as <em>Click to "
"focus</em>. If an active window has to be chosen by the system (eg. because "
"the currently active one was closed) the window under the mouse is the "
"preferred candidate. Unusual, but possible variant of <em>Click to focus</"
"em>."
msgstr ""
"<em>Fokus √ľ√ß√ľn klik (si√ßanńĪn √ľst√ľnl√ľy√ľ):</em>Bu rejimin oxŇüarńĪ<em>Fokus √ľ√ß√ľn "
"klik</em>. ∆Źg…ôr sistem aktiv p…ônc…ôr…ôni √∂z√ľ se√ß…ôrs…ô (m…ôs…ôl…ôn, aktiv p…ônc…ôr…ô "
"bańülandńĪqda) √ľst√ľnl√ľk kursorun alrńĪndakńĪ p…ônc…ôr…ôy…ô verilir. Bir az qeyri-adi "
"olsa da <em>Fokus √ľ√ß√ľn klik</em> rejimin…ô alternativ variant kimi q…ôbul "
"olunur."

#: windows.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<em>Focus follows mouse:</em> Moving the mouse onto a window will activate "
"it. Eg. windows randomly appearing under the mouse will not gain the focus. "
"<em>Focus stealing prevention</em> takes place as usual. Think as <em>Click "
"to focus</em> just without having to actually click."
msgstr ""
"<em>Fokus si√ßanńĪ izl…ôyir:</em>Kursoru √ľz…ôrind…ô h…ôr…ôk…ôt etdirdikd…ô p…ônc…ôr…ô "
"aktivl…ôŇü…ôc…ôk. T…ôsad√ľfi kursorun altńĪna d√ľŇü…ôn p…ônc…ôr…ô fokuslanmayacaq, bel…ô "
"ki, <em>Fokusun d…ôyiŇüm…ôsin qarŇüńĪsńĪnńĪn alńĪnmasńĪ</em> adi qaydada iŇül…ôyir. Bu "
"variant <em>Fokus √ľ√ß√ľn klik</em>oxŇüayńĪr, ancaq x√ľsusi klik t…ôl…ôb olunmur."

#: windows.cpp:102
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This is mostly the same as <em>Focus follows mouse</em>. If an active window "
"has to be chosen by the system (eg. because the currently active one was "
"closed) the window under the mouse is the preferred candidate. Choose this, "
"if you want a hover controlled focus."
msgstr ""
"Bu daha √ßox<em>Fokus si√ßanńĪ izl…ôyir</em> variantńĪ kimidir. ∆Źg…ôr sistem aktiv "
"p…ônc…ôr…ôni √∂z√ľ se√ß…ôrs…ô (m…ôs., aktiv p…ônc…ôr…ô bańülandńĪqda), √ľst√ľnl√ľk kursorun "
"altńĪndakńĪ p…ônc…ôr…ôy…ô verilir. √úst√ľnd…ô saxlayark…ôn fokuslamaq √ľ√ß√ľn bu rejimi "
"se√ßin."

#: windows.cpp:105
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<em>Focus under mouse:</em> The focus always remains on the window under the "
"mouse.<br/><strong>Warning:</strong> <em>Focus stealing prevention</em> and "
"the <em>tabbox ('Alt+Tab')</em> contradict the activation policy and will "
"not work. You very likely want to use <em>Focus follows mouse (mouse "
"precedence)</em> instead!"
msgstr ""
"<em>Kursorun altńĪnda fokus:</em> H…ômiŇü…ô kursorun altńĪnda fokuslanńĪr.<br/"
"><strong>X…ôb…ôrdarlńĪq</strong> <em>Fokusun d…ôyiŇüm…ôsinin qarŇüńĪsnńĪn alńĪnmasńĪ</"
"em> v…ô <em>baŇülńĪq qutusu ('Alt+Tab')</em> aktivl…ôŇüdirm…ô qaydasńĪna ziddir v…ô "
"iŇülńĪm…ôz.Bunun …ôv…ôzin…ô siz <em>Fokus si√ßanńĪ izl…ôyir</em>variantńĪnńĪ iŇül…ôtm…ôk "
"ist…ôy…ô bil…ôrsiniz."

#: windows.cpp:108
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"<em>Focus strictly under mouse:</em> The focus is always on the window under "
"the mouse (in doubt nowhere) very much like the focus behavior in an "
